# Per-developer xcconfig override (DEVELOPMENT_TEAM etc).
# Configs/Debug.xcconfig and Configs/Release.xcconfig are committed templates
# with empty team-id fields; Configs/Local.xcconfig holds the actual ID and
# stays out of git. xcconfig include directive in Debug/Release picks it up.
Configs/Local.xcconfig

